# Deny-by-default: keep the Docker build context minimal and avoid
# accidentally baking local files (configs, fixtures, editor files, etc.).
**

# --- Allow list (what the current Dockerfile needs) ---
!.dockerignore
!Dockerfile
!Cargo.toml
!Cargo.lock
!crates/
!crates/**

# --- Defense-in-depth: never include these even under allowed paths ---
**/target/
**/*.log
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/*~
**/*.swp
**/*.swo
